biz.gabrys.easybundle

Interface BundleFactory

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    MultiplePropertyResourceBundleFactory, PropertyResourceBundleFactory

    public interface BundleFactory
    Responsible for creating new instances of Bundle and message bundle interface specified by user. The correct structure of user specified interface was described in documentation of BundleValidator class.
    Since:
    1.0
    See Also:
    Bundle, BundleValidator

    • Method Summary

      Bundle create(Class<?> interfaceClass, Locale locale)

        Creates a new instance of Bundle which implements interface interfaceClass.
